      "id": "PopularPost22471",
      "post_content": "One of the earliest combat tricks in Magic was putting [Lure](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lure) on a [Thicket Basilisk](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thicket Basilisk) and attacking your opponent. Prior to 4th edition changes, Fog was an effective means to counter such an attack (for one turn anyway). 4th edition cleaned Fog up so-to-speak, removing the clunky \"otherwise affect any creature as a result of an attack or block\" clause.",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost22471\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">One of the earliest combat tricks in Magic was putting <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lure\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lure\">Lure</a> on a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Thicket Basilisk\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thicket Basilisk\">Thicket Basilisk</a> and attacking your opponent.  Prior to 4th edition changes, Fog was an effective means to counter such an attack (for one turn anyway).  4th edition cleaned Fog up so-to-speak, removing the clunky \"otherwise affect any creature as a result of an attack or block\" clause.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '22471'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (9/8/2009 8:37:19 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png